        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "If Kordo is in play:"
        }
      ],
      "color": "red"
    },
    {
      "type": "blockquote",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Kordo\u2019s eyes light up, and he moves off toward the being. He\npauses at the tree, then points to where a small branch has\nbeen half broken. Beyond that, some blades of grass have been\nbent over. Without a word, Kordo slinks off through the brush,\nbeckoning you to follow."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Add 5"
        },
        {
          "type": "span",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "icon",
              "icon": "progress",
              "color": "black"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "to A Trick of the Light."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Otherwise, read:"
        }
      ],
      "color": "red"
    },
    {
      "type": "blockquote",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "You look for impressions in the ground or broken twigs, for\nsomething\u2014anything\u2014to give evidence of this strange being.\nThis would really interest an experienced tracker like Kordo\ndown at Lone Tree."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
